and forth from Busan.

327
00:29:42,323 --> 00:29:47,495
So did you come to Seoul to see Ms.
Kang while you went to school in Busan?

328
00:29:48,454 --> 00:29:49,830
Yeah, every week.

329
00:29:49,914 --> 00:29:51,540
