was another friend...

462
00:39:25,363 --> 00:39:26,406
I mean...

463
00:39:27,574 --> 00:39:32,537
I just figured that
you already knew.

464
00:39:32,621 --> 00:39:33,955
Yeah, well...

465
00:39:34,039 --> 00:39:35,540
I know her mom left her

466
00:39:35,624 --> 00:39:39,169
