00:47:41,609 --> 00:47:42,986
What?

561
00:47:43,069 --> 00:47:44,737
Be real.

562
00:47:44,821 --> 00:47:47,198
You're being overly
self-conscious.

563
00:47:47,657 --> 00:47:51,536
